oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (navy and brown on light blue) featuring the Bluebird Cafe 2010, established in 1982. Poster features woodcuts of guitars and a bird. This poster was reprinted in 2010. Poster printed after the original edition are known as "restrikes."
